Hello Colin,

The javadoc for CrawlScope.addSeed() says, &quot;this method is *not* 
sufficient to get the new seed scheduled in the Frontier for crawling -- 
it only affects the Scope&#39;s seed record (and decisions which flow from 
seeds).&quot;

I haven&#39;t tested this, but inspecting the code would lead me to suggest 
trying CrawlJob.importUri(tweetUrl, true, true). (If your instance of 
CrawlJob isn&#39;t handy, you can probably get it via 
Heritrix.getSingleInstance().getJobHandler().getCurrentJob().)

Noah


